* {{magenta|r}} [[rat ruler]]

===EvilHack===
EvilHack introduces a few new rats:

* {{monsymlink|enormous rat}}
* {{monsymlink|rodent of unusual size}}

[[Rat King (EvilHack)|The Rat King]] of EvilHack is not a rodent like his SLASH'EM counterpart, but has many wererat-like traits minus the ability to shift to rat form.

===Hack'EM===
